Saint Don Perrion.

205
00:23:31,601 --> 00:23:33,650
Génial.

206
00:23:35,418 --> 00:23:37,436
Ok.

207
00:23:46,618 --> 00:23:49,356
Allez, Lana, décroche.

208
00:23:50,104 --> 00:23:52,799
